com.cyc.kb

Interface KbIndividual

  • All Superinterfaces:
    KbObject, KbTerm
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    BinaryPredicate, Context, KbFunction, KbPredicate, Relation

    public interface KbIndividual
extends KbTerm
    The top-level interface for Cyc #$Individuals. KbIndividual contrasts with KbCollection.
